in energy embedded in exported goods, and imported goods. A positive value indicates that a country is a net importer; a negative value indicates that a country is a net exporter.","createdAt":"2021-11-09T09:36:24.000Z","updatedAt":"2021-11-09T10:17:30.000Z","code":null,"coverage":"","timespan":"","datasetId":5403,"sourceId":21238,"shortUnit":null,"display":{"name":"Net energy embedded in traded goods","unit":"terawatt-hours","shortUnit":"TWh","includeInTable":true,"numDecimalPlaces":0},"columnOrder":0,"originalMetadata":null,"datasetName":"Consumption-based energy (Kulionis, 2021)","s_id":21238,"s_name":"Calculated by Viktoras Kulionis, based on the EXIOBASE v3.8.2 database","source":{"id":21238,"name":"Calculated by Viktoras Kulionis, based on the EXIOBASE v3.8.2 database","dataPublishedBy":"Calculated by Viktoras Kulionis, based on the EXIOBASE v3.8.2 database","dataPublisherSource":"","link":"https://zenodo.org/record/5589597#.YYf3EdnMK_0","retrievedData":"","additionalInfo":"Consumption-based (trade-adjusted) energy use can be calculated from data published in the EXIOBASE v3.8.2 database using a multi-regional input-output (MRIO) model.\n\nThis MRIO model uses data on the quantity of goods traded, and the country-specific energy intensity of producing those goods to estimate the amount of energy embodied in exported goods, and in imported goods. \n\nConsumption-based (trade-adjusted) energy use is then calculated as domestic energy use minus energy embodied in exported goods, plus imported goods.\n\nThis trade-adjusted energy use data was calculated by <a href=\"https://baug.ethz.ch/en/department/people/staff/personen-detail.MjY1MDUz.TGlzdC82NzksLTU1NTc1NDEwMQ==.html\">Viktoras Kulionis</a> using this approach.\n\nThe EXIOBASE v3.8.2 database is available online: https://zenodo.org/record/5589597#.YYf3EdnMK_0.\n\nWe have calculated per capita metrics by combining this data with population data from the UN World Population Prospects: https://population.un.org/wpp/\n\n"}}},"entityKey":{"1":{"name":"United Kingdom","code":"GBR"},"2":{"name":"Ireland","code":"IRL"},"3":{"name":"France","code":"FRA"},"4":{"name":"Belgium","code":"BEL"},"5":{"name":"Netherlands","code":"NLD"},"6":{"name":"Germany","code":"DEU"},"7":{"name":"Switzerland","code":"CHE"},"8":{"name":"Italy","code":"ITA"},"9":{"name":"Spain","code":"ESP"},"10":{"name":"Sweden","code":"SWE"},"11":{"name":"Poland","code":"POL"},"12":{"name":"Russia","code":"RUS"},"13":{"name":"United States","code":"USA"},"14":{"name":"Japan","code":"JPN"},"23":{"name":"Australia","code":"AUS"},"24":{"name":"Austria","code":"AUT"},"37":{"name":"Brazil","code":"BRA"},"39":{"name":"Bulgaria","code":"BGR"},"44":{"name":"Canada","code":"CAN"},"70":{"name":"Turkey","code":"TUR"},"81":{"name":"South Africa","code":"ZAF"},"83":{"name":"Slovenia","code":"SVN"},"85":{"name":"Slovakia","code":"SVK"},"92":{"name":"Romania","code":"ROU"},"95":{"name":"Portugal","code":"PRT"},"102":{"name":"Norway","code":"NOR"},"113":{"name":"Mexico","code":"MEX"},"119":{"name":"Lithuania","code":"LTU"},"122":{"name":"Latvia","code":"LVA"},"127":{"name":"South Korea","code":"KOR"},"136":{"name":"Indonesia","code":"IDN"},"137":{"name":"India","code":"IND"},"138":{"name":"Hungary","code":"HUN"},"149":{"name":"Greece","code":"GRC"},"155":{"name":"Finland","code":"FIN"},"156":{"name":"Estonia","code":"EST"},"161":{"name":"Denmark","code":"DNK"},"162":{"name":"Czechia","code":"CZE"},"163":{"name":"Cyprus","code":"CYP"},"165":{"name":"Croatia","code":"HRV"},"171":{"name":"China","code":"CHN"},"198":{"name":"Taiwan","code":"TWN"},"210":{"name":"Luxembourg","code":"LUX"},"212":{"name":"Malta","code":"MLT"}}}